<br>
Our DoT chants are especially powerful now that the &quot;kiting penalty&quot; has been removed - they now do full damage.  Once you get the second chant at 38, you can do an amazing amount of damage pretty quickly.  At 46 you're starting to watch stuff just melt away while you kite it.<br>
<br>
Hope this helps!<br>
<br>
